# GitHub Linguist: exclude retired/generated content from the repo's
# language stats bar, so it reflects the active implementation (Python)
# rather than the retired Rust+Tauri prototype or generated HTML.
#
# gemini_poc/ is a retired Rust+Tauri prototype (see .agents/AGENTS.md —
# "do not add new code there") — not the active implementation.
gemini_poc/** linguist-vendored
*.rs linguist-vendored

# HTML here is either the retired prototype's frontend or generated
# artifacts (coverage reports, telemetry dashboards), not source we want
# counted as a "language" in the repo stats.
*.html linguist-vendored
